Args: active_beam: List[(tokens, score)] - current hypotheses completed: List[(tokens, score)] - finished sequences beam_size: int - k
Returns: (new_active, new_completed, done_flag) """ new_active = [] newly_completed = []
for hypothesis, score in active_beam: if hypothesis[-1] == EOS_TOKEN_ID: newly_completed.append((hypothesis, score)) else: new_active.append((hypothesis, score))
# Sort completed by score (descending) and add to list newly_completed.sort(key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True) completed.extend(newly_completed) completed.sort(key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)
# Check termination conditions done = (len(new_active) == 0) or \ (len(completed) >= beam_size and completed[beam_size-1][1] >= best_active_score(new_active))
return new_active, completed, done
